msgid "# Hy3-preview"
msgstr "# Hy3-preview"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"Hy3-preview is a Mixture-of-Experts model, with 295B total parameters, 21B "
"active parameters and 3.8B MTP layer parameters, developed by the Tencent Hy"
" Team. It is the first model trained on Tencent rebuilt infrastructure. It "
"improves significantly on complex reasoning, instruction following, context "
"learning, coding, and agent tasks."
msgstr ""
"Hy3-preview "
"是一个混合专家模型，总参数量为295B，激活参数量为21B，MTP层参数量为3.8B，由腾讯混元团队开发。它是首个在腾讯重建基础设施上训练的模型。在复杂推理、指令遵循、上下文学习、编码和智能体任务方面有显著提升。"

msgid ""
"This guide records the verified vLLM Ascend serving path for Hy3-preview on "
"one Atlas A3 16-NPU node. The verified default path is TP16 + EP + MTP + "
"ACLGraph."
msgstr ""
"本指南记录了在单个 Atlas A3 16-NPU 节点上，针对 Hy3-preview 已验证的 vLLM Ascend 服务路径。已验证的默认路径为"
" TP16 + EP + MTP + ACLGraph。"

msgid "## Supported Features"
msgstr "## 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型支持的特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- Hugging Face: [tencent/Hy3-preview](https://huggingface.co/tencent/Hy3-preview)\n"
"- ModelScope: [Tencent-Hunyuan/Hy3-preview](https://modelscope.cn/models/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hy3-preview)\n"
"- GitCode: [tencent_hunyuan/Hy3-preview](https://ai.gitcode.com/tencent_hunyuan/Hy3-preview)"
msgstr ""
"- Hugging Face：[tencent/Hy3-preview](https://huggingface.co/tencent/Hy3-preview)\n"
"- ModelScope：[Tencent-Hunyuan/Hy3-preview](https://modelscope.cn/models/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hy3-preview)\n"
"- GitCode：[tencent_hunyuan/Hy3-preview](https://ai.gitcode.com/tencent_hunyuan/Hy3-preview)"

msgid ""
"Download or mount the checkpoint to a path shared by the runtime container, "
"for example `/models/Hy3-preview`."
msgstr "将检查点下载或挂载到运行容器共享的路径，例如 `/models/Hy3-preview`。"

msgid "### Hardware"
msgstr "### 硬件"

msgid ""
"The verified configuration uses one Atlas A3 node with 16 NPUs and 64 GB HBM"
" per NPU. The real-weight run used about 58 GB process memory per NPU after "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"已验证的配置使用一个 Atlas A3 节点，包含16个NPU，每个NPU拥有64 GB HBM。实际权重运行在启动后，每个NPU使用了约58 "
"GB的进程内存。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid ""
"You can use our official docker image to run Hy3-preview directly. For Atlas"
" A3 machines, select the image variant with the `-a3` suffix. The official "
"image already includes the vLLM and vLLM Ascend runtime needed for the "
"verified serving path."
msgstr ""
"您可以直接使用我们的官方 Docker 镜像来运行 Hy3-preview。对于 Atlas A3 机器，请选择带有 `-a3` "
"后缀的镜像变体。官方镜像已包含已验证服务路径所需的 vLLM 和 vLLM Ascend 运行时。"

msgid ""
"In addition, if you don't want to use the docker image as above, you can "
"also build all from source:"
msgstr "此外，如果您不想像上面那样使用 Docker 镜像，也可以从源码构建所有组件："

msgid ""
"- Install `vllm-ascend` from source, refer to "
"[installation](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/docs/source/installation.md)."
msgstr ""
"- 从源码安装 `vllm-ascend`，请参考[安装指南](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/docs/source/installation.md)。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 单节点部署"

msgid "Run `vllm serve` from `/workspace`."
msgstr "在 `/workspace` 目录下运行 `vllm serve`。"

msgid ""
"- `--enable-ep-weight-filter` is optional. It skips expert weights that do not belong to the local EP rank during loading, reducing disk and host-memory pressure for very large MoE checkpoints. We recommend keeping it enabled.\n"
"- Tool calling and reasoning are service interfaces declared in the Hy3 README, so it is recommended to pass the corresponding `hy_v3` parsers by default."
msgstr ""
"- `--enable-ep-weight-filter` 是可选的。它在加载时跳过不属于本地 EP 等级的专家权重，从而减少非常大的 MoE 检查点的磁盘和主机内存压力。建议保持启用。\n"
"- 工具调用和推理是 Hy3 README 中声明的服务接口，因此建议默认传递相应的 `hy_v3` 解析器。"

