msgid "### Lightweight Online Benchmark"
msgstr "### 轻量级在线基准测试"

msgid ""
"The following numbers are from a real-weight smoke benchmark on one Atlas A3"
" 16-NPU node, using TP16 + EP + MTP + ACLGraph. The benchmark used `vllm "
"bench serve`, random prompts, output length 128, `--max-concurrency 1`, "
"`--temperature 0`, and 4 requests per input length. These numbers are "
"functional performance evidence, not tuned throughput limits."
msgstr ""
"以下数据来自单个 Atlas A3 16-NPU 节点上的实际权重冒烟基准测试，使用了 TP16 + EP + MTP + "
"ACLGraph。基准测试使用了 `vllm bench serve`、随机提示、输出长度 128、`--max-concurrency "
"1`、`--temperature 0`，每个输入长度发送 4 个请求。这些数据是功能性能的证明，而非调优后的吞吐量上限。"

msgid ""
"| Random input length | Success / total | Mean TTFT (ms) | Mean TPOT (ms) | Output throughput (tok/s) | Total token throughput (tok/s) |\n"
"| --- | --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n"
"| 1,024 | 4 / 4 | 484.64 | 30.10 | 29.71 | 270.90 |\n"
"| 4,096 | 4 / 4 | 1379.41 | 30.24 | 24.52 | 811.99 |\n"
"| 16,384 | 4 / 4 | 2604.58 | 30.43 | 19.79 | 2554.65 |"
msgstr ""
"| Random input length | Success / total | Mean TTFT (ms) | Mean TPOT (ms) | Output throughput (tok/s) | Total token throughput (tok/s) |\n"
"| --- | --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n"
"| 1,024 | 4 / 4 | 484.64 | 30.10 | 29.71 | 270.90 |\n"
"| 4,096 | 4 / 4 | 1379.41 | 30.24 | 24.52 | 811.99 |\n"
"| 16,384 | 4 / 4 | 2604.58 | 30.43 | 19.79 | 2554.65 |"

msgid "## Known Limitations"
msgstr "## 已知限制"

msgid ""
"- The model config supports 262,144 tokens, but this guide only verifies 32,768-token serving. Larger contexts require a separate capacity validation.\n"
"- Formal AISBench accuracy results are pending and should be added only after a real benchmark run."
msgstr ""
"- 模型配置支持 262,144 个 token，但本指南仅验证了 32,768 个 token 的服务。更大的上下文需要单独进行容量验证。\n"
"- 正式的 AISBench 精度结果待定，应在实际基准测试运行后添加。"
